			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<span class="fb_share"><fb:like href="http://blog.midtowncomics.com/wanted-married-comic-book-store/5442/" layout="button_count"></fb:like></span><p>To celebrate the wedding of The X-Men&#8217;s Northstar and Kyle Jinadu in Marvel’s Astonishing X-Men #51, Midtown Comics is looking for a comic loving, same-sex couple who would be interested in getting married in our store on June 20th for a special event! Email us at <a  href="mailto:media@midtowncomics.com">media@midtowncomics.com</a></p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-5456" title="AstonishingXMen wedding pic" src="http://blog.midtowncomics.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/AstonishingXMen-wedding-pic.jpg" alt="" width="334" height="459" /></p>
<p><a  href="http://www.facebook.com/events/228181340617562/">Astonishing X-Men writer Marjorie M. Liu will be signing at Midtown Comics Downtown on June 6th from 6-7! Click for details</a></p>
<address> Volunteering to be married at this event does not guarantee that you will be selected to participate.  Midtown Comics reserves the right to choose or not to choose a couple from those who volunteer. All potential volunteers must contact Midtown Comics via e-mail at <a  href="mailto:media@midtowncomics.com">media@midtowncomics.com</a> by June 7<sup>th</sup>. No volunteers will be accepted after that date.</address>
